room_title: Escape room "Secrets of the Woods" by Cracked in Wausau
room_address: 4613, Ste C, Camp Phillips Rd Weston, WI 54476
room_description:
Your friends, Shane and Amanda set off on their annual camping trip to the great Northwoods of Wisconsin. There has been no contact with them ever since. People are starting to fear the worst...
You and your rescue team have forged into the wilderness and found their campsite. It's getting late into the evening, and upon arrival, something doesn't feel right. In this wild adventure, it is up to you and your team to discover the truth of Shane and Amanda's disappearance before time runs out.
